title: O'Neill x Kyle NG Fall Winter  15/16 Collaboration
description: O’Neill has joined forces with renowned LA-based designer Kyle NG for a second season of the stunning collaboration. Kyle NG, the man at the helm of Farm Tactics, is known for his conceptual vision, weaving together past and present inspired by the Whole Earth vibe of the Bay Area in the 1960s. In his designs for O’Neill, he puts forward his modern twist on the classic California surf lifestyle and vintage surf trend.
